import React, {useEffect} from 'react'
import "./NavBar.css"
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"
import { Dropdown } from "react-bootstrap"

const NavBar = () => {

const changeOnOver=() => {
  const element= document.getElementsByClassName("flex-menu")[0]

  element.style.border ="2px blue solid"
}

  return (
    <>
        <Navbar bg="info" variant="info">
        <Container>
         
          <Nav className="me-auto">
            <Link to="/"> Portfolio</Link>
            <Link to="/cv"> Mon CV </Link>
            <Link to="/UseEffectcompo"> Blog </Link>
            <Link to="/html-css"> HTML/CSS</Link>
            <Link to="/compteur"> Compteur </Link>
            <Link to="/liste"> Liste </Link>
            <Link to="/toggles"> Toggle </Link>
            <Link to="/object"> Object </Link>
            </Nav>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>

            <Dropdown>
            <Dropdown.Toggle variant="dark" id="dropdown-basic">
              React.js
            </Dropdown.Toggle>

            <Dropdown.Menu>
              <Dropdown.Item  as={Link} to="/Compteur" >Compteur useEffect</Dropdown.Item>
              <Dropdown.Item as={Link} to="/Liste">Action</Dropdown.Item>
              <Dropdown.Item  as={Link} to="/Toogles" >Compteur useEffect</Dropdown.Item>
              <Dropdown.Item  as={Link} to="/Object" >Compteur useEffect</Dropdown.Item>
            </Dropdown.Menu>
          </Dropdown>

            

       
    </>
  )
}

export default NavBar
